snippet: The Taliban leaders released to Qatar in exchange for Sgt. Bowe Bergdahl have suddenly eclipsed the other Famous Five in Gitmo, the plotters of the attacks of September 11, 2001.
abstract: The Taliban leaders released to Qatar in exchange for Sgt. Bowe Bergdahl have suddenly eclipsed the other Famous Five in Gitmo, the plotters of the attacks of September 11, 2001.

headline.main: To Some, Taliban Prisoners Are Gitmo's Most Famous Five
